Hi!

The agenda for the upcoming SLC meeting, the order in which they will be
taken up and the time limit for the same are as follows 

8:00 pm
1. Ratification of Speaker's Committee Core
2. Ratification of Speaker Review Committee

8:05 pm
3. Clarification regarding the status of the Amendment to the Constitution
4. Rules and Procedures for Committee

8:45 pm
5. SAC Wish List  Committee formation if necessary
6. Certification exam for GSB

9:00 pm
7. Policy on Disqualification of Legislators
8. Attendance for BCs and GenSecs
9. Resolution on Hostel and Department Council Meetings

9:30 pm
10. Formation of a AdHoc Committee for Constitution Reading
11. Discussion/Committee formation on Art of Living

The Venue for this meeting is ICSR Hall 3. Please do attend!

